author: Al Jazeera
title: China approves two coronavirus vaccines for human trials
description: Experimental COVID-19 treatments to go ahead in China as it grapples with imported cases from neighbouring Russia.
content:
China has approved early-stage human tests for two experimental coronavirus vaccines as it battles to contain imported cases and prevent a second wave of COVID-19.
